- ✓ Training-free routing via pre-execution spectral diagnostics
- ✓ Explicit stability radius constraints and perturbation bounds
- ✓ PAC-Bayes generalization certification
- ✓ Deterministic, coarse-grained block-level routing (no per-head dynamic switching)
- ✓ Single-GPU deployment with strict overhead accounting
- ✓ Rigorous ablations and sensitivity analyses

**Feasibility**: All experiments are single-GPU friendly, use standard libraries (PyTorch, Lanczos), and require only small unlabeled calibration sets.

